WEBVTT


00:00:00.220 --> 00:00:04.560
The day I realised that you can work so hard and still be poor

00:00:04.580 --> 00:00:07.520
is the day I started praying for God's Grace.

00:00:08.100 --> 00:00:12.400
Hey, there are things that you really cannot logically understand

00:00:14.300 --> 00:00:18.380
because life is a very spiritual experience.

00:00:18.381 --> 00:00:21.721
If you, if you focus on the physical, Aah,

00:00:21.900 --> 00:00:23.720
you losing it, you losing it.

00:00:24.420 --> 00:00:27.940
You can work very hard for years and still be in the same place

00:00:27.941 --> 00:00:29.461
without changing your, your, your,

00:00:29.462 --> 00:00:30.641
your situation.

00:00:30.700 --> 00:00:35.189
It's very important to ask for God's Grace in everything you do.
